

Installation:

> reconf.sh
> configure 
options of configure:
--help to see all options
--prefix
by default the path installation is /usr/local/, to define it use --prefix
  --prefix=/siconos_path_install

if you do not want to run unitary test suites, and have not installed cppUnit, use flag '--disable-cppunit'

> make

> make install


export PATH=$PATH:/siconos_path_install/bin

> siconos -h

> siconos BouncingBall/BouncingBall.cpp
